ActCanada Labour Code
PrecisReappointment of MICHELE A. PINEAU of Ottawa, Ontario, to be a Vice-Chairperson of the Canada Industrial Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years, on a full-time basis; and orders that MICHELE A. PINEAU be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act; effective January 1, 2003.
